Additional Use Grant Details

PRODUCTION USE requires a valid commercial license:

1. **Professional License - $79/month**
   - Self-hosted deployment
   - Unlimited users
   - All Professional features (MFA, OAuth Provider, GitHub Integration, Webhooks, etc.)
   - Email support (48-hour response time)
   - Use for your own products/services

2. **Enterprise License - $499/month**
   - Everything in Professional, plus:
   - Passkeys/WebAuthn, SAML SSO, SCIM Directory Sync (when available)
   - Priority support (24/7, 4-hour response time)
   - Dedicated account manager
   - Custom contract terms

DEVELOPMENT & EVALUATION use is FREE:
- ✅ Development and testing environments
- ✅ Proof-of-concept projects
- ✅ Educational purposes
- ✅ Contributing to the project

PERMITTED production use (with valid license):
- ✅ Using Truxe to authenticate users of your SaaS product
- ✅ Using Truxe for your company's internal applications
- ✅ Using Truxe for your e-commerce site's customer authentication
- ✅ Building a mobile app that uses Truxe for authentication
- ✅ Using Truxe for your game's player authentication

RESTRICTED use (requires special authorization):
- ❌ Offering "Truxe-as-a-Service" to other companies without authorization
- ❌ Creating a managed Truxe hosting business competing with Truxe Cloud
- ❌ Reselling Truxe licenses or hosting as your primary business

For managed cloud hosting, see Truxe Cloud (coming Q1 2026).

---

License Enforcement

**Current (Q4 2025):** Trust-based compliance. We trust you to honor the license terms.

**Future (Q2 2026):** License key validation will be introduced for production deployments.
- Development/testing will remain FREE - no changes
- Production will require TRUXE_LICENSE_KEY environment variable
- 3-month notice will be provided before enforcement begins
- Existing users will receive grace period for migration

